# Test Folder

Test suites live here. The default tooling is **gdUnit4**:

```bash
godot --headless -s res://addons/gdUnit4/bin/gdUnit4Cli.gd -a res://test/
```

Mirror the `src/` structure — a test for `src/domains/player/Movement.gd` belongs at `test/domains/player/test_movement.gd`. Follow Red/Green TDD where possible: a failing test must exist before the production code that satisfies it.

Delete this `.gitkeep` once real test files are added.
